Package GUI

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GamePanel
    This class handles all graphics that are related to the "game" so to speak.
    GameView
    The main window of the game, it handles what panels in the GUI that should be displayed at any given moment.
    HelpPanel
    Provides a panel with basic tutorials and help for players.
    InformationPanel
    One of the panels that is displayed constantly by the GameView class.
    InventoryPanel
    One of the panels that is displayed constantly by the GameView class.
    ItemIcon
    This is a label that represents an item by displaying its picture.
    QuestPanel
    When the player interacts with a civilian in the game, this panel becomes active.
    ShopPanel
    When the player interacts with a shop in the game, this panel becomes active.
    StartScreen
    Provides the user with a startscreen where he can choose if he wants to start a new game or load an existing one.
    StatisticsPanel
    A class for providing a panel for showing statistics.
